# PJ file-surface connector — env config ONLY. Never commit real values.
#
# PJ watches file surfaces for signals; each surface is one Source with its own
# env vars. (No scraping — a source reads exactly the configured endpoint.)
#
# --- Google Drive source ---
# A Files MCP server's HTTP bridge or an official Drive listing endpoint (JSON).
PJ_GOOGLE_DRIVE_URL=
# Optional bearer token. Keep it in your environment / secret store — never commit.
PJ_GOOGLE_DRIVE_TOKEN=

# --- Future sources drop in with the same contract (own env vars) ---
# PJ_ONEDRIVE_URL=
# PJ_DROPBOX_URL=
# PJ_SHAREPOINT_URL=
